(27043, 62631, 0, 1, 'Leopard''s Heart (demo 2010)', '', '2010-08-06 00:00:00', 2010, 0, 1, 7, 'I''ve been thinking, but I just can''t figure it out\r\nwith this freedom why don''t we stop being pushed around\r\nwe sure are free enough to go for what we really want\r\nso why do we still look away from the brightest star?\r\n\r\nwe have it all to get it done\r\nso stop finding things to blame your difficulties on\r\n\r\naim at the toughest mark\r\nfor the gold award of this hunt\r\nyou gotta show your leopard''s heart\r\n(leopard''s heart)\r\n\r\ndon''t say you can''t go on\r\nstand up, back in the run\r\nkeep doing it right then there could be no wrong\r\n\r\na leopard''s heart\r\nnever stops\r\n\r\nI did my thinking, but it''s hard to figure it out\r\nall the wisdom only led us to the most crowded route\r\nthey say the time is tough, but you know that''s not excuse for giving up\r\nchances may be thin but a hero won''t back down\r\n\r\njust be prepared for your time to come\r\nso that things could work out for you somehow\r\n\r\naim at the toughest mark\r\nfor the gold award of this hunt\r\nyou gotta show your leopard''s heart\r\n\r\ndon''t say you can''t go on\r\nstand up, back in the run\r\nwhen you go, you go at it hard\r\n\r\ncoz leopard''s heart\r\nrun up front\r\n\r\nall the heroes have their flaws\r\nall the stories have lost a part\r\nsituations could be tough\r\nbut some people carry on\r\nno matter who you are\r\njust show them what you are\r\n\r\naim at the toughest mark\r\nfor the gold award of this hunt\r\nyou gotta show your leopard''s heart\r\n\r\ndon''t say you can''t go on\r\nstand up, back in the run\r\nso you can burn the world with your blood\r\n\r\na leopard''s heart\r\nrunning hard\r\n\r\n(gotta show me your leopard''s heart)\r\n(on your run cannot be stopped, oh yeah)', '', 236, '', '降落傘', '思達', '陳佑', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2010-08-06 21:22:34', '2015-03-12 13:43:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(27044, 15514, 0, 1, '爸已達', '', '2010-08-06 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 5, '爸爸要出發  出發去遠方\r\n每一個晚上  都會很想家\r\n手機在漫遊  不敢打電話  \r\n傳個訊息不管到了哪兒 都要 說\r\n\r\n爸已達 爸已達\r\n布拉格天晴朗\r\n聖維塔大教堂前 和衛兵一起雄壯\r\n\r\n爸已達 爸已達\r\n飄著雨的廣場\r\n溫泉啤酒和咖啡 哪一個比較香\r\n\r\n爸已達 爸已達\r\n維也納天微涼\r\n熊布朗宮的樹牆 愛麗絲的仙境一樣\r\n\r\n爸已達 爸已達\r\n街角的McDonald\r\n一杯咖啡換一組 上廁所的密碼\r\n\r\n走在大街上 琳瑯滿目的櫥窗\r\n野玫瑰護手霜  拿破崙巧克力糖\r\n露天咖啡座  街頭藝人在唱\r\n送給女兒的薩克斯風  發不出聲卻很閃亮\r\n\r\n今天爸爸不在家  又要去遠方流浪\r\n上海東京或者Las Vegas \r\n不管到哪兒 都要 說 爸已達', '', 264, '', 'mimic', '木偶', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-08-06 22:30:27', '2015-03-12 13:43:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
